version_description: This wonderful song has some very unusual chord sequences. I have tried to capture them all except for the orchestral/noisy middle section.
Complete and well-aligned chords / short tab for chorus.
I made some minor changes throughout the song, but most important are major changes in verses, re-arranging the entire chorus and adding missing outro.

I can't take credit for determining what chords were used. I took the chords straight from a youtube video where this song's writer, Jeff Lynne, tells the viewer the exact chords used. View youtube video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O0mYVP4zR5s.
Complete chords and tab for the melody / original key and suggestion for capo 3rd fret / https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9JXugX4wZ3U.
